c: 12
v: 90
t: "Nabii Yuusuf tooboko qajjibsitak : diggah atu Yuusufuv? itte Yeey anu Yuusufuuy ah yi toobokoytaay, Yalli gibdaabinak nee yeyyeeqeeh fixiixik nee gaaboyseemit nee guneh, diggah Yallak meesiteeh gibdaabinal yisbire numuh, toysa diggah Yalli meqem abite marak galto mabaysa keenik iyye"